---
title: Panang-Style Beef Curry with Peanuts and Jasmine Rice
description: Thai red curry paste, peanut butter, garlic and coconut combine in a silky smooth curry! Spoon over fluffy jasmine and sprinkle with Thai chilis for an extra kick!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cari-panang-au-boeuf-31e2e727.jpg
